comparison_top_performers.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunity41_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; a = load "${App.Datasets.activities13_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true"; q = filter q by 'IsWon' == "true"; top3 = group q by 'User_UniqueUserName'; top3 = foreach top3 generate 'User_UniqueUserName' as 'User_UniqueUserName', sum('Amount') as 'sum_Amount'; top3 = order top3 by 'sum_Amount' desc; top3 = limit top3 3; top3_result = group top3 by 'User_UniqueUserName' left, a by 'User_UniqueUserName'; top3_result = foreach top3_result generate a.'User_UniqueUserName' as 'User', sum(a.'EventCount') as 'Event', sum(a.'CallCount') as 'Call', sum(a.'TaskCount') as 'Task', sum(a.'EmailCount') as 'Email'; top3_result = group top3_result by all; events = foreach top3_result generate "Event" as 'Activity Type', avg('Event') as 'Activity Count'; calls = foreach top3_result generate "Call" as 'Activity Type', avg('Call') as 'Activity Count'; tasks = foreach top3_result generate "Task" as 'Activity Type', avg('Task') as 'Activity Count'; emails = foreach top3_result generate "Email" as 'Activity Type', avg('Email') as 'Activity Count'; result = union events, calls, tasks, emails; result = group result by 'Activity Type'; result = foreach result generate 'Activity Type' as 'Activity Type', avg('Activity Count') as 'Top 3 Performers'; indv = filter a by {{coalesce(cell(team_activities.selection, 0, "User_UniqueUserName"), cell(Current_User.selection, 0, "User_Name")).asEquality('User_Name')}}; indv = group indv by 'EventSubtype'; indv = foreach indv generate'EventSubtype' as 'Activity Type', sum('ActivityCount') as 'Individual'; result_all = union result, indv; result_all = group result_all by 'Activity Type'; result_all = foreach result_all generate  'Activity Type', sum('Top 3 Performers') as 'Top 3 Performers', sum('Individual') as 'Individual';

comparison_indv_activities.query: a = load "${App.Datasets.activities13_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; indv = filter a by {{coalesce(cell(team_activities.selection, 0, "User_UniqueUserName"), cell(Current_User.selection, 0, "User_Name")).asEquality('User_Name')}}; q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunity41_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true"; q = filter q by 'IsWon' == "true"; q = group q by 'User_UniqueUserName'; q = foreach q generate 'User_UniqueUserName' as 'User_UniqueUserName', sum('Amount') as 'sum_Amount'; q = order q by 'sum_Amount' asc; q = limit q 3; top3 = group q by 'User_UniqueUserName' left, a by 'User_UniqueUserName'; top3 = foreach top3 generate q.'User_UniqueUserName' as 'User', sum(a.'ActivityCount') as 'ActivityCount'; result = group indv by all, top3 by all; result = foreach result generate sum(indv.'ActivityCount') - avg(top3.'ActivityCount') as 'sum_comparison'; result = foreach result generate abs('sum_comparison') as 'sum_comparison', (case when 'sum_comparison' >= 0 then "More" else "Less" end) as 'more_or_less';
